      "author": "mark.anley (Green Llamas Consulting)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi Everyone!  We just wanted to take some time to express our gratitude to the amazing app developer community out there. Your knowledge, expertise and creativity help make <a href=\"http://monday.com\">monday.com</a> the best and most flexible product available.</p>\n<p>We as system designers and implementers heavily rely on 3rd party apps to round out solutions and fill the gaps in current functionality.  I couldn’t imagine doing our jobs without you (looking at you <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/jcorrell\">@JCorrell</a>, <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/basdebruin\">@basdebruin</a>, <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/nir-jetpack\">@Nir-Jetpack</a>, <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/thomas-omnitas\">@Thomas-Omnitas</a>, <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/rob\">@rob</a>, <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/thusitha\">@thusitha</a> <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/samicaracand\">@samicaracand</a>).</p>\n<p>We’ve made a short (but ever growing) list of some of our most commonly used GO TO apps to help celebrate the awesomeness!</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/3/34301eadabf7811f4b39874ed56d5ef4fbb3c17c.png\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/3/34301eadabf7811f4b39874ed56d5ef4fbb3c17c_2_690x113.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"113\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1060×175 54.7 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Check out the full list below!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.greenllamas.com/favoritethings\">Our Favorite Things | Green Llamas</a></p>\n<p>Checkback often as we are always adding to the list to help promote the best of the best!</p>\n<p>Feel free to add your favorite apps to the list to help spread the <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/heart.png?v=12\" title=\":heart:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":heart:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>Thanks all!<br />\nMark</p><aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/1/e/1ece9165a9fa643341da747dab517948963cf89e.png\" class=\"site-icon\" width=\"369\" height=\"428\" />\n\n      <a href=\"https://www.greenllamas.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Green Llamas</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    \n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.greenllamas.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">monday.com + Green Llamas</a></h3>\n\n  <p>Green Llamas is here to help you make all your People and Projects Green.  Let us get your herds under control using the monday.com platform.</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div></div>\n</aside>\n"
